ically accurate, so correcting it back to match the source typo would introduce confusion. For the omission, the Phase E agent probably concluded that developers would understand the linking mechanism from the context of the individual sections without needing the explicit introductory sentence.\n\nBoth findings have low user impact, so `needs_improvement` should be `false`.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":28316,"cache_read_input_tokens":29902,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":28316,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"dbfe14ae-74a6-477e-af7d-9ea5121c648b","uuid":"8182c4fc-f29f-4845-be11-415d79dcd0b8"}
